ft;\"| \"Sweet Suzanne\"\n| Buzzin' Cousins\n| 68\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''[[Falling from Grace (film)|Falling from Grace]]'' soundtrack\n|-\n| 2013\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Yes We Will\"\n| [[Maria Doyle Kennedy]]\n| -\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Sing'' \n|}\n\n===Videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!| Year\n!| Title\n!| Label\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[John Prine \u2013 Live from Sessions at West 54th]]''\n| [[Oh Boy Records]] Music Video\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! style=\"width:12em;\"| Video\n! Director\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 1992\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Picture Show\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/383897/picture-show.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine : Picture Show|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016}}</ref>\n| Jim Shea\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Sweet Suzanne\" <small>(Buzzin' Cousins)\n| [[Marty Callner]]\n|-\n| 1993\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Speed Of The Sound Of Loneliness\" {{small|(featuring [[Nanci Griffith]])}}\n| [[Rocky Schenck]]\n|-\n| 1995\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ain't Hurtin' Nobody\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/103394/aint-hurtin-nobody.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine : Ain't Hurtin' Nobody|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016}}</ref>\n| Jim Shea\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Fish and Whistle (Lyric Video)\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WNuuBfWFYvQ|title=John Prine - Fish and Whistle (Lyric Video)|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019}}</ref>\n| Northman Creative\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I'm Telling You\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/1546089/im-telling-you-feat-holly-williams.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine, Holly Williams : I'm Telling You (feat. Holly Williams)|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016}}</ref><br />{{small|(featuring 